speech.p:
Resolved: That, for the purposes of any Act of the present Session to provide for cattle-grids in highways, it is expedient to authorise the payment out of moneys provided by Parliament
(a) of any increase attributable to the provisions of the said Act in the sums payable out of the Road Fund;
(b) of any increase attributable to the provisions of the said Act in the sums payable out of moneys provided by Parliament under Part I or Part I.1 of the Local Government Act, 1948."—[Mr. Barnes.]
